ClickHouse JDBC Driver
  Artifact:  com.clickhouse:clickhouse-jdbc:0.4.6 (all classifier)
  License:   Apache License 2.0
  Source:    https://github.com/ClickHouse/clickhouse-java
  Maven:     https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/com/clickhouse/clickhouse-jdbc/0.4.6/

  Note: The JAR included in the jars/ directory of this distribution is the
  official Maven Central artifact with one modification: the file
  META-INF/services/java.sql.Driver has been removed. This prevents Java's
  ServiceLoader from auto-registering the driver during JVM startup, which
  causes a class-initialization race condition in Dremio's DBCP2 connection
  pool. No source code, compiled classes, or other content has been altered.
  The original unmodified JAR can be obtained from Maven Central at the URL
  above. The installer's --driver-fetch option will download and apply this
  same patch transparently at install time if you prefer not to use the
  pre-patched JAR.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Dremio ARP (Advanced Relational Pushdown) Framework
